# Third-party: exclude all except audit-critical subdirectories.
# research-integrity-auditor: MinerU convert, evidence ledger, numeric forensics scripts.
# elis/system_modules: panel-extractor (YOLOv5), copy-move (RootSIFT/SILA), TruFor adapters.
# paperconan: GRIM/GRIMMER numeric forensics (imported via sys.path in adapter).
# All three are required at runtime — see engine/static_audit/_pipeline_steps.py (AUDITOR_ROOT)
# and engine/static_audit/adapters/paperconan_adapter/__init__.py.
third_party/AsyncReview/
third_party/deepwiki-open/
web/frontend/node_modules/
web/frontend/dist/
*.pdf
*.xlsx
*.csv

